### AmazingSim Release 12.0

We are pleased to announce the release of AmazingSim 12.0.  This new release makes AmazingSim
the **most advanced simulation tool on the planet...bar far**.  It does everything using 
state of the art technology and it is more powerful and easier to use than any competing tool.

